{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532210/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1725576275\" /><br><br><strong>The Monster King is Back!</strong><br><br>The Monster King is back and has stolen all of the Wizard's precious Artefacts. They must be retrieved! Set off on an awesome adventure to slay the Monster King and take back what is yours. Fortunately the Wizard has knowledge of all different magics, so experiment by combing them together and creating new spells. Armed with only the most powerful of arcana, defeat bosses and obtain different relics as you explore every hand-crafted room, within procedurally generated levels, filled with a huge variety of enemies.<br><br>Time of the Wizard is a culmination of the best bits from The binding of Issac, Enter the Gungeon to create the ultimate twin-stick shooter roguelike. Every run is unique from the level itself and the rooms within to the spells you cast and the Artefacts that effect them. Be warned however, the creatures of the Monster King are tough and if you end up defeated then you'll have to start all over again.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532210/extras/FeaturesPNG.png?t=1725576275\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore Unique hand-crafted rooms</strong> within procedurally generated levels. Find new enemies, items and secrets along your journey to the depths below</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Combat foes with twin-stick bullet hell action</strong> - Cast spells and exploit different enemies weaknesses to maximize your damage output.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Collect unique and fun artefacts to enhance your build.</strong> Every relic has a special effect that can completely change your run, choose wisely.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Create the spells you want to use</strong> by combining the various different elements to